# Practice Stack - Tech Stack

## Frontend Framework
- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- React 18

## UI and Styling
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui component library
- Lucide React for icons
- Mobile-first, responsive design

## State Management
- React useState/useReducer for local state
- Zustand for global client state (when needed)

## Authentication
- Custom OTP-based authentication system
- Email/SMS login without passwords

## Database
- PostgreSQL
- Prisma ORM for database access

## Key Features
- Lead Management: Capture, qualify, and convert leads with custom statuses
- Proposal Builder: Drag-and-drop sections, upload signatures, export branded PDFs
- Dynamic Pricing Engine: Configure static and per-user rates, prepayment and recurring billing
- Real-Time Dashboard: KPI cards, charts, and alerts for proposal statuses and expirations

## Key Libraries
- Zod for validation
- Axios for API requests
- date-fns for date manipulation